title: Would You Be My Girltrend 7/23: Jacksonville, Avatar 2, Taylor Swift, Halo Infinite
itunes:title: Would You Be My Girltrend 7/23: Jacksonville, Avatar 2, Taylor Swift, Halo Infinite
description:
On this edition of Would You Be My Girltrend Miles and DJ Danl discuss part of the RNC in Jacksonville getting cancelled, Avatar 2 has been pushed back, Taylor Swift is releasing her 8th studio album tonight at midnight (!!!), and Halo Infinite showed some new gameplay at the Xbox presentation.
